&lt;p&gt;Includes substantial refactoring and clarification of logic and definitions around `ulog` and `tlog`. Refactoring largely focuses on UpdateLog and HdfsUpdateLog. There is no anticipated change in existing behavior, other than that the `dir` parameter to the `&amp;lt;updateLog&amp;gt;` element in `solrconfig.xml`, which has long been silently ignored, will now be respected&lt;/p&gt;

